DESCRIPTION:POST 3 — How to help without leaving your couch\n\nPost text
 :\nNot ready to go bee hunting? You can still help. SaveTheHives has 1\,15
 0+ historical hive records from 2008–2017 that nobody has checked on in 
 years. If one happens to be near you\, confirming whether it's still activ
 e takes under a minute — tap a pin\, tap Validate\, done.\n\nEvery confi
 rmation is real data for researchers. savethehives.org\n\nImage: SaveTheHi
 ves_map_screenshot_cropped.jpg (live screenshot of the map around Raleigh\
 , browser chrome cropped out — captured Jul 20 2026)\n\nAlt text: "Scree
 nshot of the SaveTheHives map showing hive pin locations around Raleigh\, 
 NC."\n\nLink: keep the trailing URL as-is — no preview card will generat
 e since a photo is attached. The plain text is the only way readers get th
 e link.\n\nSuggested timing: launch week\, day 6–7\n\nFull copy in FACEB
 OOK_STARTER_PACK.md §3.
LOCATION:facebook.com/savethehives
STATUS:CONFIRMED
END:VEVENT
