DESCRIPTION:POST 5 — Call for founding contributors\n\nPost text:\nSaveT
 heHives is entirely volunteer-run — no funding\, no ad budget\, just peo
 ple who care about wild bees. If you're a beekeeper\, a Scout leader\, a h
 iker\, or just someone who likes a good treasure hunt\, we could use you. 
 Log a hive\, confirm one that's already logged\, or just share this with s
 omeone who'd like it. savethehives.org 🐝\n\nImage: logo.jpg — closes 
 the launch sequence on the brand mark itself\, appropriate for a "join us"
  post\n\nAlt text: "SaveTheHives logo."\n\nLink: keep the trailing URL as-
 is — no preview card will generate since a photo is attached.\n\nSuggest
 ed timing: week 2\, day 5–6\n\nAfter this\, ongoing weekly cadence begin
 s per FACEBOOK_STARTER_PACK.md §5 — Mon/Wed/Sun rotation\, delivered vi
 a the savethehives-fb-weekly-digest scheduled task each Sunday evening.\n\
 nFull copy in FACEBOOK_STARTER_PACK.md §3.
LOCATION:facebook.com/savethehives
STATUS:CONFIRMED
